<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <meta name="description" content="Nova Fantasia - Le serveur Minecraft Anarchie ultime. Survie, PvP, pillage, zéro règle. Rejoignez l'expérience No Wipe dès maintenant.">
    <meta name="keywords" content="Minecraft, Anarchie, Serveur, PvP, Survie, Nova Fantasia, FalixNodes, No Rules">
    <meta name="author" content="Nova Fantasia">
    <title>Nova Fantasia | Serveur Minecraft Anarchie</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Montserrat:wght@400;500;600;800;900&family=Share+Tech+Mono&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        /* =========================================
           VARIABLES ET RESET DE BASE
           ========================================= */
        :root {
            --primary-color: #ff4d4d;
            --primary-hover: #cc3d3d;
            --primary-dim: rgba(255, 77, 77, 0.15);
            --bg-color: #060606;
            --surface-color: #101010;
            --surface-light: #1a1a1a;
            --text-main: #ffffff;
            --text-muted: #888888;
            --border-color: #222222;
            --accent-glow: rgba(255, 77, 77, 0.35);
            --accent-glow-strong: rgba(255, 77, 77, 0.6);
            --gold: #f0a500;
            --green: #4caf50;
        }

        *, *::before, *::after { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }

        html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }

        body {
            font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;
            background-color: var(--bg-color);
            color: var(--text-main);
            display: flex;
            overflow-x: hidden;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        a { text-decoration: none; color: inherit; }
        ul { list-style: none; }
        img { max-width: 100%; height: auto; display: block; }

        /* SCROLLBAR PERSONNALISÉE */
        ::-webkit-scrollbar { width: 6px; }
        ::-webkit-scrollbar-track { background: var(--bg-color); }
        ::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb { background: #2a2a2a; border-radius: 3px; }
        ::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb:hover { background: var(--primary-color); }

        /* =========================================
           ANIMATIONS CSS GLOBALES
           ========================================= */
        @keyframes fadeUp {
            from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(50px); }
            to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
        }
        @keyframes fadeIn {
            from { opacity: 0; }
            to { opacity: 1; }
        }
        @keyframes pulseGlow {
            0%, 100% { box-shadow: 0 0 10px var(--accent-glow), 0 0 20px var(--accent-glow); }
            50% { box-shadow: 0 0 20px var(--accent-glow-strong), 0 0 40px var(--accent-glow-strong); }
        }
        @keyframes pulseGlowText {
            0%, 100% { text-shadow: 0 0 10px var(--accent-glow); }
            50% { text-shadow: 0 0 25px var(--accent-glow-strong), 0 0 50px rgba(255, 77, 77, 0.3); }
        }
        @keyframes slideInRight {
            from { opacity: 0; transform: translateX(60px); }
            to { opacity: 1; transform: translateX(0); }
        }
        @keyframes slideInLeft {
            from { opacity: 0; transform: translateX(-60px); }
            to { opacity: 1; transform: translateX(0); }
        }
        @keyframes scanline {
            0% { top: -5%; }
            100% { top: 105%; }
        }
        @keyframes glitch1 {
            0%, 90%, 100% { clip-path: none; transform: none; }
            91% { clip-path: inset(20% 0 60% 0); transform: translateX(-4px); }
            93% { clip-path: inset(40% 0 40% 0); transform: translateX(4px); }
            95% { clip-path: inset(60% 0 20% 0); transform: translateX(-2px); }
        }
        @keyframes glitch2 {
            0%, 88%, 100% { clip-path: none; transform: none; opacity: 0; }
            89% { clip-path: inset(10% 0 70% 0); transform: translateX(5px); opacity: 0.8; color: #ff4d4d; }
            91% { clip-path: inset(50% 0 30% 0); transform: translateX(-5px); opacity: 0.8; color: #00ffff; }
        }
        @keyframes borderSpin {
            0% { transform: rotate(0deg); }
            100% { transform: rotate(360deg); }
        }
        @keyframes modalPop {
            from { transform: scale(0.85) translateY(20px); opacity: 0; }
            to { transform: scale(1) translateY(0); opacity: 1; }
        }
        @keyframes fadeOutRight {
            to { opacity: 0; transform: translateX(110%); }
        }
        @keyframes typewriter {
            from { width: 0; }
            to { width: 100%; }
        }
        @keyframes blink {
            0%, 100% { border-right-color: var(--primary-color); }
            50% { border-right-color: transparent; }
        }
        @keyframes floatY {
            0%, 100% { transform: translateY(0px); }
            50% { transform: translateY(-12px); }
        }
        @keyframes shake {
            0%, 100% { transform: translateX(0); }
            10%, 30%, 50%, 70%, 90% { transform: translateX(-4px); }
            20%, 40%, 60%, 80% { transform: translateX(4px); }
        }
        @keyframes countUp {
            from { opacity: 0; transform: scale(0.5); }
            to { opacity: 1; transform: scale(1); }
        }
        @keyframes heroLineGrow {
            from { width: 0; }
            to { width: 80px; }
        }
        @keyframes neonFlicker {
            0%, 19%, 21%, 23%, 25%, 54%, 56%, 100% {
                text-shadow: 0 0 5px var(--primary-color), 0 0 20px var(--accent-glow);
            }
            20%, 24%, 55% {
                text-shadow: none;
            }
        }

        .reveal {
            opacity: 0;
            transform: translateY(40px);
            transition: all 0.85s cubic-bezier(0.25, 0.46, 0.45, 0.94);
        }
        .reveal.active {
            opacity: 1;
            transform: translateY(0);
        }
        .reveal-left {
            opacity: 0;
            transform: translateX(-40px);
            transition: all 0.85s cubic-bezier(0.25, 0.46, 0.45, 0.94);
        }
        .reveal-left.active {
            opacity: 1;
            transform: translateX(0);
        }
        .reveal-right {
            opacity: 0;
            transform: translateX(40px);
            transition: all 0.85s cubic-bezier(0.25, 0.46, 0.45, 0.94);
        }
        .reveal-right.active {
            opacity: 1;
            transform: translateX(0);
        }

        /* =========================================
           CANVAS BACKGROUND (PARTICULES CENDRES)
           ========================================= */
        #particle-canvas {
            position: fixed;
            top: 0; left: 0;
            width: 100%; height: 100%;
            z-index: 0;
            pointer-events: none;
            opacity: 0.5;
        }

        /* =========================================
           SIDEBAR PREMIUM
           ========================================= */
        .sidebar {
            width: 270px;
            background: linear-gradient(180deg, #0e0e0e 0%, #080808 100%);
            height: 100vh;
            position: fixed;
            border-right: 1px solid #1e1e1e;
            padding: 30px 18px;
            z-index: 200;
            overflow-y: auto;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            transition: transform 0.4s cubic-bezier(0.25, 0.8, 0.25, 1);
        }
        .sidebar::after {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: 0; right: 0;
            width: 1px;
            height: 100%;
            background: linear-gradient(180deg, transparent, var(--primary-color), transparent);
            opacity: 0.4;
        }

        .sidebar-brand {
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: 900;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 2px;
            text-align: center;
            padding-bottom: 25px;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #1a1a1a;
            position: relative;
        }
        .sidebar-brand span { color: var(--primary-color); animation: neonFlicker 5s infinite; }
        .sidebar-brand .brand-dot {
            display: block;
            width: 6px; height: 6px;
            background: var(--primary-color);
            border-radius: 50%;
            margin: 8px auto 0 auto;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px var(--primary-color);
        }

        .sidebar-menu { flex-grow: 1; }
        .sidebar-menu li { margin-bottom: 6px; }
        .menu-label {
            font-size: 10px;
            font-weight: 800;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 2px;
            color: #444;
            padding: 12px 15px 6px 15px;
        }
        .menu-link {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 12px;
            padding: 11px 15px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            color: var(--text-muted);
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            transition: all 0.25s ease;
            border-left: 2px solid transparent;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        .menu-link::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            inset: 0;
            background: var(--primary-color);
            opacity: 0;
            transition: opacity 0.25s;
        }
        .menu-link:hover, .menu-link.active {
            background: rgba(255, 77, 77, 0.06);
            color: var(--text-main);
            border-left-color: var(--primary-color);
            padding-left: 20px;
        }

        details.menu-dropdown { cursor: pointer; color: var(--text-muted); font-weight: 600; font-size: 0.9rem; }
        details.menu-dropdown summary {
            padding: 11px 15px;
            list-style: none;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            border-radius: 8px;
            border-left: 2px solid transparent;
            transition: 0.25s;
        }
        details.menu-dropdown[open] summary {
            color: var(--primary-color);
            background: rgba(255, 77, 77, 0.06);
            border-left-color: var(--primary-color);
        }
        .dropdown-content { padding: 4px 0 8px 12px; }
        .dropdown-content a {
            display: block;
            padding: 7px 10px 7px 14px;
            font-size: 13px;
            color: #666;
            transition: 0.2s;
            border-left: 1px solid #1e1e1e;
            margin-left: 8px;
        }
        .dropdown-content a:hover {
            color: var(--text-main);
            border-left-color: var(--primary-color);
            padding-left: 18px;
        }

        .sidebar-footer {
            margin-top: auto;
            padding-top: 20px;
            border-top: 1px solid #1a1a1a;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 0.75rem;
            color: #3a3a3a;
        }
        .sidebar-footer .status-dot {
            display: inline-block;
            width: 6px; height: 6px;
            background: #4caf50;
            border-radius: 50%;
            margin-right: 6px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 6px #4caf50;
            animation: pulseGlow 2s infinite;
        }

        .menu-toggle { display: none; }
        .burger-btn {
            display: none;
            position: fixed;
            top: 18px; left: 18px;
            z-index: 1001;
            font-size: 20px;
            cursor: pointer;
            background: var(--surface-color);
            padding: 8px 12px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            border: 1px solid var(--border-color);
            box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.7);
        }

        /* =========================================
           CONTENU PRINCIPAL
           ========================================= */
        .main-content {
            margin-left: 270px;
            flex: 1;
            min-height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            position: relative;
            z-index: 1;
        }
        section { padding: 110px 6%; position: relative; z-index: 2; }

        .section-title {
            font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 3vw, 2.8rem);
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 70px;
            font-weight: 900;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 3px;
            position: relative;
        }
        .section-title::after {
            content: '';
            display: block;
            width: 50px; height: 3px;
            background: var(--primary-color);
            margin: 16px auto 0 auto;
            border-radius: 2px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px var(--accent-glow);
            animation: heroLineGrow 1s ease forwards;
        }
        .section-title span { color: var(--primary-color); }

        /* =========================================
           SECTION HERO — GLITCH PREMIUM
           ========================================= */
        .hero {
            min-height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            text-align: center;
            background: radial-gradient(ellipse at 50% 40%, rgba(60, 10, 10, 0.7) 0%, var(--bg-color) 65%);
            border-bottom: 1px solid #181818;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        .hero-scanline {
            position: absolute;
            left: 0; width: 100%; height: 3px;
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, rgba(255, 77, 77, 0.15), transparent);
            animation: scanline 8s linear infinite;
            pointer-events: none;
        }
        .hero-badge {
            background: rgba(255, 77, 77, 0.07);
            border: 1px solid rgba(255, 77, 77, 0.5);
            color: var(--primary-color);
            padding: 8px 22px;
            border-radius: 50px;
            font-size: 12px;
            font-weight: 800;
            letter-spacing: 4px;
            margin-bottom: 28px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            animation: pulseGlow 3s infinite;
        }

        .hero-title-wrap { position: relative; display: inline-block; }
        .hero h1 {
            font-size: clamp(3rem, 7vw, 6rem);
            font-weight: 900;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            line-height: 1.0;
            animation: fadeUp 0.9s ease-out forwards;
            letter-spacing: -1px;
        }
        .hero h1 .line1 { display: block; color: #fff; }
        .hero h1 .line2 { display: block; color: var(--primary-color); animation: pulseGlowText 4s infinite; }

        /* GLITCH EFFECT */
        .glitch-wrap { position: relative; }
        .glitch-wrap::before, .glitch-wrap::after {
            content: attr(data-text);
            position: absolute;
            top: 0; left: 0;
            width: 100%; height: 100%;
            font-size: inherit;
            font-weight: inherit;
            text-transform: inherit;
            letter-spacing: inherit;
            line-height: inherit;
        }
        .glitch-wrap::before {
            animation: glitch1 7s infinite;
            color: #ff4d4d;
        }
        .glitch-wrap::after {
            animation: glitch2 7s infinite;
            color: #00ffff;
        }

        .hero p {
            color: var(--text-muted);
            font-size: clamp(1rem, 1.4vw, 1.2rem);
            max-width: 620px;
            margin: 28px auto 50px auto;
            animation: fadeUp 1.1s ease-out forwards;
            font-weight: 500;
            line-height: 1.8;
        }

        /* BOUTON IP */
        .ip-container { animation: fadeUp 1.3s ease-out forwards; }
        .server-ip-box {
            background: rgba(15, 15, 15, 0.9);
            border: 1px solid #2a2a2a;
            padding: 18px 45px;
            border-radius: 50px;
            font-size: clamp(1rem, 1.5vw, 1.35rem);
            font-weight: 800;
            font-family: 'Share Tech Mono', monospace;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: all 0.35s cubic-bezier(0.25, 0.8, 0.25, 1);
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 15px;
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
            color: white;
        }
        .server-ip-box::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            inset: -2px;
            border-radius: 50px;
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--primary-color), #ff9944, var(--primary-color));
            background-size: 200% 100%;
            z-index: -1;
            opacity: 0;
            transition: opacity 0.3s;
            animation: borderSpin 3s linear infinite;
        }
        .server-ip-box:hover::before { opacity: 1; }
        .server-ip-box:hover {
            background: #0d0d0d;
            transform: translateY(-4px) scale(1.03);
            box-shadow: 0 15px 35px rgba(255, 77, 77, 0.25);
        }
        .server-ip-box:active { transform: translateY(1px) scale(0.98); }
        .ip-hint { margin-top: 14px; font-size: 0.82rem; color: #444; }

        /* =========================================
           SECTION FEATURES / ABOUT
           ========================================= */
        .about-section {
            background: linear-gradient(180deg, #080808, #0c0c0c);
            border-bottom: 1px solid #181818;
        }
        .about-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
            gap: 28px;
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }
        .about-card {
            background: #0b0b0b;
            padding: 38px 32px;
            border-radius: 16px;
            border: 1px solid #1c1c1c;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
            transition: all 0.4s cubic-bezier(0.25, 0.8, 0.25, 1);
            cursor: default;
        }
        .about-card::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: 0; left: 0;
            width: 100%; height: 3px;
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--primary-color), #ff9944);
            transform: scaleX(0);
            transform-origin: left;
            transition: transform 0.4s ease;
        }
        .about-card::after {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            bottom: -60px; right: -60px;
            width: 150px; height: 150px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(255,77,77,0.06) 0%, transparent 70%);
            transition: all 0.5s ease;
        }
        .about-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-10px);
            box-shadow: 0 25px 50px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.7);
            border-color: rgba(255, 77, 77, 0.25);
        }
        .about-card:hover::before { transform: scaleX(1); }
        .about-card:hover::after { width: 250px; height: 250px; bottom: -80px; right: -80px; }
        .about-card h3 { font-size: 1.4rem; margin-bottom: 16px; font-weight: 800; }
        .about-card p { color: var(--text-muted); font-size: 0.95rem; line-height: 1.8; }
        .icon-large {
            font-size: 2.2rem;
            display: block;
            margin-bottom: 18px;
            transition: transform 0.3s;
        }
        .about-card:hover .icon-large { transform: scale(1.2) rotate(-5deg); animation: floatY 2s ease infinite; }

        /* =========================================
           SECTION GALERIE PREMIUM
           ========================================= */
        .gallery-section { background: #060606; }
        .gallery-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
            gap: 16px;
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }
        .gallery-item {
            border-radius: 12px;
            overflow: hidden;
            position: relative;
            aspect-ratio: 16/9;
            background: var(--surface-light);
            border: 1px solid #1c1c1c;
            cursor: pointer;
        }
        .gallery-item img {
            width: 100%; height: 100%;
            object-fit: cover;
            transition: transform 0.6s cubic-bezier(0.25, 0.8, 0.25, 1), filter 0.4s;
            filter: brightness(0.6) saturate(0.8);
        }
        .gallery-item:hover img { transform: scale(1.1); filter: brightness(0.9) saturate(1.1); }
        .gallery-overlay {
            position: absolute;
            inset: 0;
            background: linear-gradient(to top, rgba(0,0,0,0.95) 0%, rgba(0,0,0,0.3) 50%, transparent 100%);
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: flex-start;
            justify-content: flex-end;
            padding: 20px;
            opacity: 0;
            transition: opacity 0.35s;
        }
        .gallery-item:hover .gallery-overlay { opacity: 1; }
        .gallery-overlay span {
            font-weight: 800;
            font-size: 1.05rem;
            transform: translateY(15px);
            transition: transform 0.35s cubic-bezier(0.25, 0.8, 0.25, 1);
        }
        .gallery-overlay .gallery-tag {
            font-size: 0.7rem;
            color: var(--primary-color);
            font-weight: 800;
            letter-spacing: 2px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            transform: translateY(20px);
            transition: transform 0.35s 0.05s cubic-bezier(0.25, 0.8, 0.25, 1);
            margin-bottom: 6px;
        }
        .gallery-item:hover .gallery-overlay span,
        .gallery-item:hover .gallery-overlay .gallery-tag {
            transform: translateY(0);
        }
        /* Highlight : première grande image */
        .gallery-item.highlight {
            grid-column: span 2;
        }
        @media (max-width: 700px) { .gallery-item.highlight { grid-column: span 1; } }

        /* =========================================
           SECTION STATISTIQUES ULTRA PREMIUM
           ========================================= */
        .stats-section { background: #070707; border-top: 1px solid #181818; }
        .stats-header {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: flex-end;
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 0 auto 50px auto;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            gap: 20px;
        }
        .stats-header-text h2 { font-size: clamp(1.6rem, 3vw, 2.5rem); font-weight: 900; text-transform: uppercase; }
        .stats-header-text p { color: var(--text-muted); margin-top: 8px; font-size: 0.95rem; }
        .refresh-btn-manual {
            background: var(--primary-color);
            color: white;
            border: none;
            padding: 14px 28px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;
            font-weight: 800;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: all 0.3s;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 10px;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
        }
        .refresh-btn-manual:hover {
            background: var(--primary-hover);
            transform: translateY(-3px);
            box-shadow: 0 12px 25px rgba(255, 77, 77, 0.3);
        }
        .stats-container {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
            gap: 24px;
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }
        .stat-card {
            background: linear-gradient(145deg, #0e0e0e, #080808);
            padding: 40px 30px;
            border-radius: 16px;
            border: 1px solid #1c1c1c;
            text-align: center;
            transition: all 0.4s cubic-bezier(0.25, 0.8, 0.25, 1);
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        .stat-card::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            bottom: 0; left: 0; right: 0;
            height: 2px;
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, var(--primary-color), transparent);
            opacity: 0;
            transition: opacity 0.4s;
        }
        .stat-card:hover { border-color: rgba(255,77,77,0.3); transform: translateY(-6px); box-shadow: 0 20px 40px rgba(255,77,77,0.1); }
        .stat-card:hover::before { opacity: 1; }
        .stat-icon { font-size: 38px; margin-bottom: 18px; display: block; filter: drop-shadow(0 0 8px rgba(255,255,255,0.15)); }
        .stat-card h3 { color: #555; font-size: 0.85rem; margin-bottom: 14px; font-weight: 700; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 2px; }
        .stat-card p { font-size: 2.3rem; font-weight: 900; color: white; }
        .stat-card.clickable { cursor: pointer; }
        .stat-card.clickable .click-hint {
            display: block;
            font-size: 0.75rem;
            color: var(--primary-color);
            font-weight: 700;
            margin-top: 10px;
            opacity: 0;
            transition: opacity 0.3s;
        }
        .stat-card.clickable:hover .click-hint { opacity: 1; }

        /* =========================================
           SECTION FAQ PREMIUM
           ========================================= */
        .faq-section { background: linear-gradient(180deg, #0a0a0a, #060606); }
        .faq-container { max-width: 820px; margin: 0 auto; }
        .faq-item {
            background: #0b0b0b;
            border: 1px solid #1e1e1e;
            border-radius: 12px;
            margin-bottom: 12px;
            overflow: hidden;
            transition: all 0.3s;
        }
        .faq-item.active { border-color: rgba(255, 77, 77, 0.4); box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(255,77,77,0.1); }
        .faq-question {
            padding: 20px 25px;
            cursor: pointer;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            font-weight: 700;
            font-size: 1rem;
            transition: background 0.2s;
            user-select: none;
        }
        .faq-question:hover { background: rgba(255,255,255,0.02); }
        .faq-icon { font-size: 1.4rem; color: var(--primary-color); transition: transform 0.4s cubic-bezier(0.25, 0.8, 0.25, 1); flex-shrink: 0; }
        .faq-item.active .faq-icon { transform: rotate(45deg); }
        .faq-answer { max-height: 0; overflow: hidden; transition: max-height 0.45s ease, padding 0.3s; padding: 0 25px; color: var(--text-muted); line-height: 1.8; font-size: 0.95rem; }
        .faq-item.active .faq-answer { max-height: 300px; padding: 0 25px 22px 25px; }

        /* =========================================
           SECTION CONTACT FORMULAIRE — NOUVEAU
           ========================================= */
        .contact-section {
            background: #080808;
            border-top: 1px solid #181818;
        }
        .contact-wrapper {
            max-width: 1100px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
            gap: 60px;
            align-items: start;
        }
        @media (max-width: 900px) { .contact-wrapper { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } }

        .contact-info h3 { font-size: 1.8rem; font-weight: 900; margin-bottom: 16px; }
        .contact-info p { color: var(--text-muted); line-height: 1.8; margin-bottom: 35px; }

        .contact-email-box {
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 14px;
            background: #0d0d0d;
            border: 1px solid #252525;
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 18px 25px;
            transition: all 0.3s;
            margin-bottom: 35px;
            cursor: pointer;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
            width: 100%;
        }
        .contact-email-box::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            left: 0; top: 0; bottom: 0;
            width: 3px;
            background: linear-gradient(180deg, var(--primary-color), #ff9944);
            border-radius: 3px 0 0 3px;
        }
        .contact-email-box:hover {
            border-color: rgba(255,77,77,0.3);
            box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(255,77,77,0.1);
            transform: translateY(-2px);
        }
        .email-icon { font-size: 1.5rem; flex-shrink: 0; }
        .email-details { flex: 1; }
        .email-label { font-size: 0.72rem; font-weight: 700; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 2px; color: #555; margin-bottom: 3px; }
        .email-address { font-family: 'Share Tech Mono', monospace; color: var(--primary-color); font-size: 0.95rem; font-weight: 600; }
        .email-copy-hint { font-size: 0.72rem; color: #444; margin-top: 2px; }

        .contact-tags { display: flex; gap: 10px; flex-wrap: wrap; margin-top: 20px; }
        .contact-tag {
            background: rgba(255,77,77,0.07);
            border: 1px solid rgba(255,77,77,0.2);
            color: #888;
            padding: 6px 14px;
            border-radius: 50px;
            font-size: 0.78rem;
            font-weight: 600;
        }

        /* FORMULAIRE CONTACT */
        .contact-form-wrap {
            background: #0b0b0b;
            border: 1px solid #1e1e1e;
            border-radius: 20px;
            padding: 36px;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        .contact-form-wrap::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: 0; left: 0; right: 0;
            height: 2px;
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, var(--primary-color), transparent);
        }
        .contact-form-wrap h4 { font-size: 1.2rem; font-weight: 800; margin-bottom: 8px; }
        .contact-form-wrap .form-desc { color: var(--text-muted); font-size: 0.88rem; margin-bottom: 28px; }

        .form-group { margin-bottom: 18px; }
        .form-group label {
            display: block;
            font-size: 0.8rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 1.5px;
            color: #666;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
        }
        .form-group input,
        .form-group select,
        .form-group textarea {
            width: 100%;
            background: #080808;
            border: 1px solid #1e1e1e;
            border-radius: 10px;
            padding: 14px 18px;
            color: white;
            font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            transition: all 0.3s;
            outline: none;
            resize: none;
            appearance: none;
            -webkit-appearance: none;
        }
        .form-group input::placeholder,
        .form-group textarea::placeholder { color: #333; }
        .form-group input:focus,
        .form-group select:focus,
        .form-group textarea:focus {
            border-color: rgba(255,77,77,0.5);
            box-shadow: 0 0 0 3px rgba(255,77,77,0.07);
            background: #0a0a0a;
        }
        .form-group select { cursor: pointer; }
        .form-group select option { background: #111; }

        .form-row { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 16px; }
        @media (max-width: 500px) { .form-row { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } }

        .submit-btn {
            width: 100%;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary-color), #cc2200);
            color: white;
            border: none;
            padding: 16px 30px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;
            font-weight: 800;
            font-size: 0.95rem;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: all 0.3s;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 1.5px;
            margin-top: 6px;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        .submit-btn::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: 50%; left: 50%;
            width: 0; height: 0;
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.12);
            border-radius: 50%;
            transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
            transition: width 0.5s, height 0.5s;
        }
        .submit-btn:hover::before { width: 300px; height: 300px; }
        .submit-btn:hover { transform: translateY(-3px); box-shadow: 0 15px 30px rgba(255,77,77,0.3); }
        .submit-btn:active { transform: translateY(1px); }

        .form-note { font-size: 0.75rem; color: #444; text-align: center; margin-top: 14px; }

        /* =========================================
           FOOTER ULTRA PREMIUM
           ========================================= */
        footer {
            background: #040404;
            padding: 80px 6% 40px 6%;
            border-top: 1px solid #181818;
            margin-top: auto;
            position: relative;
            z-index: 10;
        }
        footer::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: 0; left: 6%; right: 6%;
            height: 1px;
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, var(--primary-color), transparent);
            opacity: 0.4;
        }
        .footer-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 2fr 1fr 1fr;
            gap: 50px;
            max-width: 1100px;
            margin: 0 auto 50px auto;
        }
        @media (max-width: 900px) { .footer-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; } }
        @media (max-width: 600px) { .footer-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } }

        .footer-col h4 { font-size: 0.85rem; color: #666; margin-bottom: 20px; font-weight: 800; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 2px; }
        .footer-col ul li { margin-bottom: 10px; color: var(--text-muted); font-size: 0.9rem; }
        .footer-col ul li a { transition: 0.2s; }
        .footer-col ul li a:hover { color: var(--primary-color); padding-left: 4px; }

        .footer-logo { font-size: 2rem; font-weight: 900; margin-bottom: 12px; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 1px; }
        .footer-logo span { color: var(--primary-color); }
        .footer-desc { color: #444; font-size: 0.88rem; line-height: 1.8; margin-bottom: 22px; }
        .footer-mail-link { color: var(--primary-color); font-size: 0.9rem; font-weight: 700; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px; }
        .footer-mail-link:hover { text-decoration: underline; }

        .social-links { display: flex; gap: 10px; margin-top: 18px; }
        .social-btn {
            width: 38px; height: 38px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            background: #111;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            border: 1px solid #222;
            transition: 0.3s;
            font-size: 1rem;
        }
        .social-btn:hover { background: var(--primary-color); border-color: var(--primary-color); transform: translateY(-3px) rotate(-5deg); }

        .footer-bottom {
            border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.04);
            padding-top: 28px;
            text-align: center;
            color: #333;
            font-size: 0.78rem;
            max-width: 900px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            line-height: 2;
        }

        /* =========================================
           TOAST — SYSTÈME NOTIFICATIONS
           ========================================= */
        .toast-container {
            position: fixed;
            bottom: 30px; right: 30px;
            z-index: 9999;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 10px;
            pointer-events: none;
        }
        .toast {
            background: #111;
            border: 1px solid #222;
            border-left: 3px solid var(--primary-color);
            padding: 14px 22px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 15px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.6);
            color: white;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 0.88rem;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 12px;
            opacity: 0;
            transform: translateX(100%);
            animation: slideInRight 0.35s forwards;
            pointer-events: all;
        }
        .toast.success { border-left-color: #4caf50; }
        .toast.error { border-left-color: var(--primary-color); }
        .toast.hide { animation: fadeOutRight 0.4s forwards; }

        /* =========================================
           MODALE JOUEURS
           ========================================= */
        .modal {
            position: fixed;
            inset: 0;
            background: rgba(0,0,0,0.88);
            z-index: 3000;
            display: none;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
        }
        .modal-content {
            background: #0d0d0d;
            width: 90%; max-width: 520px;
            border-radius: 18px;
            border: 1px solid #222;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 30px 80px rgba(0,0,0,0.9);
            animation: modalPop 0.4s cubic-bezier(0.175, 0.885, 0.32, 1.275) forwards;
        }
        .modal-header {
            padding: 22px 28px;
            background: rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
            border-bottom: 1px solid #1a1a1a;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
        }
        .modal-title { font-size: 1.3rem; font-weight: 800; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px; }
        .close-btn {
            cursor: pointer;
            font-size: 20px;
            color: #555;
            transition: 0.3s;
            width: 30px; height: 30px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            border-radius: 50%;
            background: #111;
            border: 1px solid #222;
        }
        .close-btn:hover { color: white; background: var(--primary-color); border-color: var(--primary-color); transform: rotate(90deg); }
        #player-list { max-height: 430px; overflow-y: auto; padding: 18px 25px; }
        .player-item {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: space-between;
            padding: 14px;
            background: rgba(0,0,0,0.25);
            border: 1px solid #1a1a1a;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            transition: 0.25s;
        }
        .player-item:hover { background: rgba(255,255,255,0.03); border-color: #2a2a2a; transform: translateX(4px); }
        .player-info { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 14px; }
        .player-info img { border-radius: 6px; box-shadow: 0 0 12px rgba(0,0,0,0.6); }
        .player-name { font-weight: 700; }

        /* BACK TO TOP */
        #backToTop {
            position: fixed;
            bottom: 30px; right: 30px;
            background: #111;
            color: white;
            width: 46px; height: 46px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            font-size: 20px;
            cursor: pointer;
            border: 1px solid #222;
            box-shadow: 0 8px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.5);
            opacity: 0;
            visibility: hidden;
            transition: all 0.3s;
            z-index: 998;
        }
        #backToTop.visible { opacity: 1; visibility: visible; }
        #backToTop:hover { background: var(--primary-color); border-color: var(--primary-color); transform: translateY(-4px); }

        /* =========================================
           RESPONSIVE
           ========================================= */
        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .sidebar { transform: translateX(-100%); }
            .main-content { margin-left: 0; }
            .burger-btn { display: block; }
            #menu-toggle:checked ~ .sidebar { transform: translateX(0); box-shadow: 15px 0 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.9); }
            section { padding: 70px 5%; }
            .toast-container, #backToTop { bottom: 20px; right: 20px; }
        }
        @media (max-width: 480px) {
            .hero h1 { font-size: 2.4rem; }
            .server-ip-box { font-size: 0.95rem; padding: 14px 22px; }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

<canvas id="particle-canvas"></canvas>

<input type="checkbox" id="menu-toggle" class="menu-toggle">
<label for="menu-toggle" class="burger-btn">☰</label>

<!-- SIDEBAR -->
<aside class="sidebar">
    <div class="sidebar-brand">
        Nova<br><span>Fantasia</span>
        <span class="brand-dot"></span>
    </div>
    <ul class="sidebar-menu">
        <li><div class="menu-label">Navigation</div></li>
        <li><a href="#home" class="menu-link active">🏠 Accueil</a></li>
        <li><a href="#about" class="menu-link">📖 L'Expérience</a></li>
        <li><a href="#gallery" class="menu-link">📸 Galerie</a></li>
        <li><a href="#stats" class="menu-link">📊 Statistiques</a></li>
        <li><a href="#faq" class="menu-link">❓ F.A.Q</a></li>
        <li><a href="#contact" class="menu-link">✉️ Contact</a></li>

        <li style="margin-top: 18px;">
            <div class="menu-label">Communauté</div>
        </li>
        <li>
            <details class="menu-dropdown">
                <summary>⚔️ Événement ▼</summary>
                <div class="dropdown-content">
                    <a href="/arene">🔥 L'Arène</a>
                </div>
            </details>
        </li>
        <li>
            <details class="menu-dropdown">
                <summary>👥 Réseaux ▼</summary>
                <div class="dropdown-content">
                    <a href="https://discord.com/invite/9hEamDNMj" target="_blank">💬 Discord Officiel</a>
                    <a href="https://www.youtube.com/@adam44-y1y" target="_blank">📺 Game Revive (YT)</a>
                    <a href="https://m.twitch.tv/game_revive44" target="_blank">💜 Game Revive (Twitch)</a>
                    <a href="https://www.youtube.com/@noghosttt" target="_blank">📺 Noghosttt (YT)</a>
                    <a href="https://m.twitch.tv/noghosttt" target="_blank">💜 Noghosttt (Twitch)</a>
                </div>
            </details>
        </li>
    </ul>
    <div class="sidebar-footer">
        <span class="status-dot"></span> Serveur 1.20+ No Wipe
    </div>
</aside>

<!-- MAIN -->
<main class="main-content">

    <!-- HERO -->
    <section class="hero" id="home">
        <div class="hero-scanline"></div>
        <div class="hero-badge">💀 Anarchie Extrême — No Wipe</div>
        <div class="hero-title-wrap">
            <h1>
                <span class="line1">L'Anarchie à</span>
                <span class="line2 glitch-wrap" data-text="l'État Pur.">l'État Pur.</span>
            </h1>
        </div>
        <p>Ni règles, ni admins, ni pitié. Forge ton destin, trahis tes alliés, détruit des empires. Bienvenue dans l'enfer qui ne se réinitialise jamais.</p>

        <div class="ip-container">
            <button class="server-ip-box" onclick="copyIP()" title="Copier l'adresse IP">
                <span style="color: var(--primary-color);">⚔️</span>
                <span id="server-ip-text">novafantasia.falixsrv.me</span>
                <span style="color: #333; font-size: 0.8rem;">📋</span>
            </button>
            <div class="ip-hint">Cliquez pour copier et rejoindre le chaos</div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- FEATURES / ABOUT -->
    <section id="about" class="about-section">
        <h2 class="section-title reveal">Les Lois du <span>Chaos</span></h2>
        <div class="about-grid">
            <div class="about-card reveal">
                <span class="icon-large">🔪</span>
                <h3>Zéro Règle Absolue</h3>
                <p>Le grief, le vol, les trahisons et le PvP sauvage sont l'essence même du serveur. Tout ce qui n'est pas un hack ruinant le serveur techniquement est permis. Fais confiance à tes propres armes.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="about-card reveal" style="transition-delay: 0.12s;">
                <span class="icon-large">🗺️</span>
                <h3>Jamais Réinitialisé</h3>
                <p>Notre promesse No Wipe garantit que tes ruines, tes monuments et tes cratères resteront gravés pour toujours. Laisse ton empreinte dans ce monde dévasté à jamais.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="about-card reveal" style="transition-delay: 0.24s;">
                <span class="icon-large">🔥</span>
                <h3>Économie de Guerre</h3>
                <p>Pas de monnaie virtuelle, pas de shop. La seule valeur est celle des ressources que tu parviens à extraire, cacher ou voler. L'économie est 100% menée par les joueurs.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- GALERIE -->
    <section id="gallery" class="gallery-section">
        <h2 class="section-title reveal">Vestiges & <span>Guerres</span></h2>
        <div class="gallery-grid">
            <div class="gallery-item highlight reveal">
                <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1606169493527-31368297b4dd?auto=format&fit=crop&q=80&w=900&h=506" alt="Ruines du spawn">
                <div class="gallery-overlay">
                    <div class="gallery-tag">📍 Zone 0,0</div>
                    <span>Les ruines du spawn</span>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="gallery-item reveal" style="transition-delay: 0.1s;">
                <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1519074069444-1ba4fff66d16?auto=format&fit=crop&q=80&w=600&h=337" alt="Combat PvP">
                <div class="gallery-overlay">
                    <div class="gallery-tag">⚔️ PvP</div>
                    <span>Combat au Nether</span>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="gallery-item reveal" style="transition-delay: 0.2s;">
                <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1542840410-3092f99611a3?auto=format&fit=crop&q=80&w=600&h=337" alt="Paysage ravagé">
                <div class="gallery-overlay">
                    <div class="gallery-tag">💣 Destruction</div>
                    <span>Le cratère 0,0</span>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- STATS -->
    <section id="stats" class="stats-section">
        <div class="stats-header reveal">
            <div class="stats-header-text">
                <h2>État du <span style="color:var(--primary-color);">Serveur</span></h2>
                <p>Connexion directe avec les serveurs FalixNodes — données en temps réel.</p>
            </div>
            <button class="refresh-btn-manual" onclick="manualRefresh()" id="refresh-btn">
                <span>🔄</span> Forcer l'actualisation
            </button>
        </div>
        <div class="stats-container">
            <div class="stat-card reveal">
                <span class="stat-icon">📡</span>
                <h3>Statut Réseau</h3>
                <p id="status-text" style="color: #ff4d4d; font-size: 1.8rem;">Recherche...</p>
            </div>
            <div class="stat-card clickable reveal" onclick="showPlayers()" style="transition-delay: 0.1s;">
                <span class="stat-icon">💀</span>
                <h3>Survivants Connectés</h3>
                <p id="players-text">— / —</p>
                <span class="click-hint">→ Voir la liste</span>
            </div>
            <div class="stat-card reveal" style="transition-delay: 0.2s;">
                <span class="stat-icon">⚙️</span>
                <h3>Version Requise</h3>
                <p id="version-text">1.20+</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- FAQ -->
    <section id="faq" class="faq-section">
        <h2 class="section-title reveal">Questions <span>Fréquentes</span></h2>
        <div class="faq-container reveal">
            <div class="faq-item">
                <div class="faq-question" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">
                    <span>Puis-je utiliser un client cheat (Hacks) ?</span>
                    <span class="faq-icon">+</span>
                </div>
                <div class="faq-answer">
                    <p>L'utilisation de clients modifiés (X-Ray, KillAura, Flight) dépend de la politique exacte du moment. Généralement sur un serveur purement anarchique, le principe est de ne pas intervenir — MAIS tout hack causant des crashs délibérés (Lag machines) est passible d'un bannissement réseau.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="faq-item">
                <div class="faq-question" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">
                    <span>Le serveur va-t-il fermer ou reset la map ?</span>
                    <span class="faq-icon">+</span>
                </div>
                <div class="faq-answer">
                    <p>Non. Nova Fantasia a été conçu avec la promesse d'une map intemporelle. La taille du monde augmentera, mais les chunks générés ne seront jamais effacés par les administrateurs.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="faq-item">
                <div class="faq-question" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">
                    <span>Est-il possible d'acheter un grade ou des avantages ?</span>
                    <span class="faq-icon">+</span>
                </div>
                <div class="faq-answer">
                    <p>Absolument pas. Nova Fantasia est strictement anti-Pay-To-Win. Il n'y a pas de boutique, pas de kits, pas de commandes VIP. Tout le monde naît nu et misérable sur ce serveur.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="faq-item">
                <div class="faq-question" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">
                    <span>Comment rejoindre le serveur pour la première fois ?</span>
                    <span class="faq-icon">+</span>
                </div>
                <div class="faq-answer">
